{"tid":1327548,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"起訴運輸署署長","createTime":"2019-07-17T15:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T15:59:38.000Z","uid":77666,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"16863f2104e93d94da2b925af9dc6aa9fd5701db","tid":1327548,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:41:04.000Z","msg":"岩岩見到有個post講 銅鑼灣告士打道圍欄全拆<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1327152/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1327152/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n圍欄對於行人及駕駛者之間起左重大既安全作用 若果拆圍欄而引起本身不必要既交通意外 或者行人覺得安全性大大減低 應該可以向政府追討損失及追究運輸署署長基於什麼原因去拆除圍欄 <br />\n不過小弟就諗唔到向邊個部門投訴 第1 比較可行係運房局 因為運輸署係under運房局 不過佢地應該就意見接受 態度照舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第2 若果想再勁d的話 唔知可唔可以直接司法覆核運輸署署長呢個決定 到時運輸署署長就不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望有專家可以出來解釋下 小弟既諗法可唔可行<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff4606ae8f2a2f735f1b314c0b6d8fe55a53f86","tid":1327548,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:41:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"57f39f289f821eaaf34ea786bddb8968a5688937","tid":1327548,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:43:27.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9560d0c7c65b8c75b80d0947d44ec88735f33d65","tid":1327548,"uid":39517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"可以係度u turn<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021ce264996bd796789147f841e25200fd0eda10","tid":1327548,"uid":45305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:45:31.000Z","msg":"如果咁易就拆得，咁之前整黎做乜？<br />\n咁樣係咪浪費公帑？"},{"pid":"17c826a0613f33d98a3abcd9738ffaa9f4e538d7","tid":1327548,"uid":77666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9560d0c7c65b8c75b80d0947d44ec88735f33d65","tid":1327548,"uid":39517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"